title: OnlyChillstep Selections #1-27 320mp3
description:
Love these selections so I thought I would put them all together for you all...

This collection includes Chillstep mixes #1-27 from OnlyChillstep's YouTube channel:

They were all downloaded at 720p (except the first few at 480p), and converted from mp4 format to 320kbps CBR mp3 with foobar2000 and LAME.  This provides essentially the utmost quality, coming from the raw mp4.  I have managed mp3 tags by providing the artist 'OnlyChillstep' and track names so it organizes well in your player.

I've found these great for studying, lucid dreaming, tripping out, etc.  Goes well with Milkdrop 2 visualizer in WinAmp!

Enjoy, and please seed to at least 100% to allow your fellow pirate the same experience!
